data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous neighborhood! This 3-bedroom, 2-bath brick all around the house, roof is like a year old. Is nestled in a desirable location near Randolph AFB and Ft. Sam (2 major military bases) and near SAMC Hospital the largest burning unit in the worldCome and view this beautiful home in Highland Farms. The interior has been professionally painted and has new carpet in all bedrooms and living room. Kitchen and dining room has new laminate flooring. Kitchen has new modern backsplash for a more modern look. Dining room has French doors that leads out to a covered porch and a large shelf storage in the back yard. This house will not last long.
